Riky Rick has been remembered as an amazing father and loving partner. Courtesy of #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Rikhado "Riky Rick" Makhado has been remembered as an amazing father and loving partner. The widow of the late award-winning hip-hop artist, businessman and fashion mogul said he was the spark that lit her soul. READ: Fans, industry peers shocked by Riky Rick's death Bianca Naidoo says Makhado always stood by her and encouraged her to be the best version of herself. A private funeral service was held on Tuesday, READ: Riky Rick to be buried on Tuesday Business partner and friend Sheldon Tatchell says they shared a special bond that grew beyond just business. He says they always encouraged one another and often spoke about situations they were facing. Tatchell says the late artist always gave the best advice.